By now you should have posted a brief update to [b][url=https://www.meetup.com/bostonphp/messages/boards/thread/53875156]Introduce Yourself[/url][/b] which will acknowledge your commitment to begin this training opportunity. Next, we will conduct three sprints over the next three weeks to complete the three courses in this learning path as follows:

[b]Sprint #1[/b] covers [b]Introduction to Career Skills in Software Development[/b]. This first of three sprints begins on May 15 and concludes on May 21, 2023. Once you complete this two-hour course you will receive a certificate of completion you can post to your linked in profile. Please share a link to your certificate below so that I can monitor participant progress. Then, proceed to the next course in this Learning Path.

